#: topic_folders/policies/privacy.md:61
msgid "We may obtain the name and email address of Other volunteers. If you choose to complete a volunteer/instructor profile, we may store your name, email address, gender, nearest airport location, organisational affiliation, occupation, ORCID ID, GitHub and Twitter handle, and personal URL."
